She hears something fall behind her.  She looks and sees Time Bomb 
out cold on the floor. "Oh no. He's passed out. I wonder what could 
have made him..." she then realized he saw the mech fluid and that 
made him loose it.  She smiled and walked over to him.  She picked 
him up and put him on teh table.  She turned to Land Mine. "Don't 
worry, he'll be OK."  She grabbed a vile from the cabnet and opened 
it. She went over tot he table and waved the vile under Time Bomb's 
nose. "He'll coma around in a second. He just can't stand the sight 
of fluid is all. He'll be fine."
